spanGrp.span: ha gabugd dabalol anin gidayiiny ha
I'm returning again to speak, me I'm called Gidayiny
Narudia kuongea tena mimi naitwa Gidayiny
gabugd dabalol anin gidayiiny gila aa gab gisiireed aa gisiireed gab gilugwend
I'm returning to speak again, me I'm called Gidayiny of Gisired, and Gisired is of Gilugwend
Narudia kuongea tena mimi naitwa Gidayiny wa gisired na gisired ni wa gilugwend
ha gabugd darug ee matatisajeeh sidahayi
I'm returning to speak about the problems we are facing
aa gagul qamn qawasch haw aa ng'asheeg gad qoendeley ng:asheeg munyasi
Until now, I'm old and problems are still continuing, bad problems
Mpaka sasa mimi ni mkubwa na mambo bado yanaendelea mambo mabaya
qamn asees ar maeney gey gematosch ge gijeeduln giyeet
Now even these areas we are stealing from each other, like we will finish each other, each for themselves
'Sasa hata maeneo sisi tunanyang''anyana kama tutamalizana wenyewe kwaon of wenyewe'
aa menal gicha qaweedees aa ng'ashanj aa qotawala gijeenus geyeet
And we don't know what will help us, this problem has ruled over us, we will kill each other
Na hatujui kitu gani kitatusaidia neno hili limetawala tutauana
as ha su seeni aa ng'asheeg munyasi ab jeed ng'anyiid
So these are all bad problems inside our country
Haya yote ni mambo mabaya ndani ya nchi
gwach qang'eedeew gayeeny qay genusaday geyeet ab masawjeeg atvqann gad eendeleyan
Those hours I started by saying in various areas in the old days we were killing each other, even now we are continuing
Saa zile nilianza kwa kusema katika mwano mbalimbali zamani tuliuana hata sasa bado tunaendeleza
aa menal gicha qaweedees anin qamn gagur gidab ha gawetees aseet gichay
And we don't know what will help us, me often I say it is only God who will help us
Na hatujui kitu gani kitatusaidia mimi huwa nasema ni mungubtu anatusaidia
aa nyiis gemoond geyeet gewasch kabileed ng'ayii
And often we don't want each other to succeed, we are a small tribe
Na huwa tunonana kijicho tupo kabila ndogo
aa nyass gemoond geyeet aa asees gemanmanees diya
And often we don't want each other to succeed, and we are squeezed together
Na huwa tunonana kijicho na sisi tumebanwa sana
